@startuml
title SLH-DSA structure - FORS certified up the hypertree (d layers)
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam linetype ortho

package "Hypertree (HT): d layers of XMSS trees" {
  [PK.root  (top XMSS root = public key)] as ROOT
  package "Layer d-1 : single XMSS tree" {
    [WOTS+ key signs root below] as L2
  }
  package "Layer 1 : 2^(d-2)h' XMSS trees" {
    [WOTS+ key signs root below] as L1
  }
  package "Layer 0 : 2^(d-1)h' XMSS trees" {
    [WOTS+ key signs FORS public key] as L0
  }
  ROOT --> L2
  L2 --> L1 : WOTS+ sig + auth path
  L1 --> L0 : WOTS+ sig + auth path
}

package "FORS (few-time, k trees of 2^a leaves)" {
  [FORS public key] as FPK
  [k revealed secrets + auth paths] as FSIG
  FPK --> FSIG
}

L0 --> FPK : WOTS+ sig certifies FORS key
FSIG --> [Message digest md] : signs

note right of ROOT
  Only PK.root (n bytes) is published.
  Everything below is regenerated
  from SK.seed on demand.
end note
@enduml
